  "metadata": {
    "name": "Disable Postfix Network Listening",
    "description": "Edit the file <tt>/etc/postfix/main.cf</tt> to ensure that only the following\n<tt>inet_interfaces</tt> line appears:\n<pre>inet_interfaces = {{{ xccdf_value(\"var_postfix_inet_interfaces\") }}}</pre>",
    "rationale": "This ensures <tt>postfix</tt> accepts mail messages\n(such as cron job reports) from the local system only,\nand not from the network, which protects it from network attack.",
